            "short": "<p><strong>Activation: </strong><span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Special Activation\" aria-label=\"Special Activation\">*</span></p><p>Gain an additional <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Special Activation\" aria-label=\"Special Activation\">r</span> at the start of combat and at the start of each of your turns, which you can use only to @UUID[Compendium.cosmere-rpg.actions.Item.6Vm9QIbIjDOeSCwq]{Dodge}. You can’t benefit from this talent while wearing armor with a deflect value of 2 or higher.</p>"
